<section class="faq-section relative overflow-hidden py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="section relative z-10">
    <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[0.82fr_1.18fr] lg:items-start">
      <div class="faq-intro-card" data-faq-anim="intro">
        <div class="pixel-scene pixel-scene-generated" aria-hidden="true"><div class="penguin-action-sprite penguin-faq-action"></div></div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Dudas frecuentes</span>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl leading-tight sm:text-4xl">
          El pingüino responde
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-3" data-faq-root>
        <details class="faq-item group" data-faq-anim="item">
          <summary class="faq-summary">¿Trabajan pedidos para empresas, colegios o cafeterías?<svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
          <div class="faq-content transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden max-h-0"><div class="faq-answer">Sí. Cotizamos según cantidad, fecha, presentación y tipo de entrega dentro de Loja.</div></div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item group" data-faq-anim="item">
          <summary class="faq-summary">¿Hacen envíos fuera de Loja?<svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
          <div class="faq-content transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden max-h-0"><div class="faq-answer">Por ahora solo dentro de Loja.</div></div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item group" data-faq-anim="item">
          <summary class="faq-summary">¿Con cuánta anticipación debo pedir?<svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
          <div class="faq-content transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden max-h-0"><div class="faq-answer">Idealmente 2 a 3 días. Pedidos grandes o personalizados: una semana.</div></div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item group" data-faq-anim="item">
          <summary class="faq-summary">¿Puedo personalizar un pastel?<svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
          <div class="faq-content transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden max-h-0"><div class="faq-answer">Sí. Revisamos idea, color, dedicatoria y tamaño por WhatsApp.</div></div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item group" data-faq-anim="item">
          <summary class="faq-summary">¿Tienen opciones sin azúcar o sin gluten?<svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
          <div class="faq-content transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden max-h-0"><div class="faq-answer">Algunas opciones se trabajan bajo pedido.</div></div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item group" data-faq-anim="item">
          <summary class="faq-summary">¿Cuáles son los métodos de pago?<svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
          <div class="faq-content transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden max-h-0"><div class="faq-answer">Efectivo o transferencia bancaria.</div></div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  import "~/scripts/faq-accordion.js";
  import "~/scripts/faq-animation.js";
</script>

<div class="ornament-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
